{
  "text": "Are you saying, then, that this power is of the spirit and not of the mind or the body? I am Ra. The work of the adept is based upon previous work with the mind and the body, else work with the spirit would not be possible on a dependable basis. With this comment we may assert the correctness of your assumption.",
